{"tid":537114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身材曲線一問","createTime":"2018-01-22T11:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T11:58:13.000Z","uid":149098,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1d4f5df8369eb3ead5775fae8159d5bd7b04ae","tid":537114,"uid":149098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"今日係gym<br />\n當每個女仔都只係著好保守嘅sports wear<br />\n見到一個好有自信嘅香港女仔著sports bra<br />\n佢身材好係佢好瘦<br />\n背面望有S shape<br />\n但側面望佢個胸係完全嘅平<br />\n個蘿都唔大<br />\n巴打點睇<br />\n<br />\n好欣賞佢嘅自信 但我一直以為有身材係有前有後<br />\n定係時代變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情願唔要心口嘅脂肪都要瘦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e69bf769b3d9697e0201f1ff82d0dd56faf3bbd","tid":537114,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"有前有後係好<br />\n<br />\n但天生冇波都冇計，肥唔代表會大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9770b46a6760024b9a816f137fc413587435c3f5","tid":537114,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"咁你細jer做唔做gym？"},{"pid":"f0a41b17378256811a2cd6e2def8f804356749d3","tid":537114,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"有自信都唔得"}]}